The Good Girl;;59;;83;;R;;Justine (Jennifer Aniston) is the good girl. Thirty years old and working in a Texas discount store, she is dissatisfied by her routine and disgusted by her lazy, pot-smoking husband. Her life is nearly at a standstill, until she suddenly notices Holden (Jake Gyllenhaal) a few cash registers away. He is young and seemingly as disaffected as she, and together the two forge a passionate connection destined to shatter everything Justine stands for, or at least thinks she does.;;Drama,Comedy;;Miguel Arteta;;2002;;Jennifer Aniston,Jake Gyllenhaal,John C. Reilly,Tim Blake Nelson,Zooey Deschanel,Mike White,Deborah Rush,John Carroll Lynch;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/good_girl